OL,3,CAccrington family hub boss says
OL,4,CNational Insurance cut not enough
OL,6,F"The 2p cut to National Insurance is
OL,7,Fdefinitely not enough, it doesn't go
OL,8,Ffar enough. It gives a bit to some but
OL,9,Fit doesn't give something to everybody.
OL,11,F"It's not going to include those who
OL,12,Fare most in need. It's only giving a
OL,13,Fbreak perhaps to those who aren't
OL,14,Fstruggling as much."
OL,16,FMeanwhile a vape manufacturer in
OL,17,FGreater Manchester says the new tax on
OL,18,Fvapes, announced in today's Budget,
OL,19,Fwill only leave vapers out of pocket,
OL,20,Fwith those who make the devices not
OL,21,Freally affected.
