OL,4,CNational Insurance cut not enough
OL,6,FMike Holliday is the regional lead for
OL,7,F88 Vape in Trafford Park. They make
OL,8,F3,000 vape devices a day.
OL,10,FMike told ITV News "Of course you want
OL,11,Fyour products to be reasonably priced
OL,12,Fon the shelf but everybody's going to
OL,13,Fbe taxed the same and so versus our
OL,14,Fcompetitors, nothing's really going to
OL,15,Fchange there. It's the consumers who
OL,16,Fare going to end up footing the bill
OL,17,Ffor it"
OL,19,FThe Government is to introduce a new
OL,20,Fon vapes in a bid to discourage non-
OL,21,Fsmokers from taking up the habit.
