OL,3,CAccrington family hub boss says
OL,4,CNational Insurance cut not enough
OL,6,FDuring his Budget speech, Chancellor
OL,7,FJeremy Hunt told the Commons he was
OL,8,Fconfirming "the introduction of an
OL,9,Fexcise duty on vaping products from
OL,10,FOctober 2026 and publishing a
OL,11,Fconsultation on its design".
OL,13,FHowever, he said that, because vapes
OL,14,F"play a positive role" in helping
OL,15,Fsmokers quit, there will also be a one-
OL,16,Foff increase in tobacco duty to ensure
OL,17,Fvaping remains cheaper than smoking.
